Product Requirement Document

   Who is going to use this application?
  
    1) Scientists involved in light chemistry, biology, geology, anatomy and environmental sciences.
    2) Students learning about spectrometry in their university curriculum (e.g. Chemistry class students)
    3) AUA lab workers (students and instructors) who want to analyse their solution and get full compound data.
   
   Why are people going to use this application?
   
    1) To get full compound data very fast, without the need of tedeous manual analysis.
    2) It can be used with any spectrometer that uses a camera as it's light sensor.
    3) The software can connect to extensive databases, and any comparison data can be found.
